In both cases, Dorsey framed Twitter's struggles to address hate speech on =
its platform not as issues of policy but of communication. And yet, as one =
former Twitter employee noted to me yesterday, Dorsey's tweetstorm itself c=
ommunicated no real information about Jones or company policy. The fact tha=
